<li><a href="http://www.esperanto.net" class="external text" title="http://www.esperanto.net" rel="nofollow">The Multi-Lingual Information Centre</a>, information and numerous Esperanto-related links in over 60 languages.</li>
<li><a href="http://claudepiron.free.fr/articles.htm" class="external text" title="http://claudepiron.free.fr/articles.htm" rel="nofollow">Articles, studies and discussion about problems of Esperanto and other international languages</a> (articles in 25 languages) by <a href="/wiki/Claude_Piron" title="Claude Piron">Claude Piron</a>.</li>
