<li><a href="http://www.skotlando.org.uk/scottish-esperanto-association/downloads" class="external text" title="http://www.skotlando.org.uk/scottish-esperanto-association/downloads" rel="nofollow">Esperanto Dvorak keyboard for Windows</a> using spare keys</li>
